Apis-mellifera

A 3-6 player game about making honey.

Bee types

Queen (Female)
Drone (male)
Worker (Female)

Necter
Pollen

Royal Jelly
Beeswax

Game board made from individual carboard hexes

bees vomit in a chain (B2B2B) of 3 different bees (game rule) before filling a honeycomb.

Worker takes one turn to fill a honeycomb.

two turns (game rule) to produce honey.

two turns to produce worker bee, after honeycomb filled by queen with larva and pollen.

one trun to produce a new honeycomb

visit five flowers to collect necter and pollen










